------ How to test Aneris?

You'll need: scala, gnome-terminal, wmctrl


o To compile Aneris, type

    make aneris
    make client

o First, start aneris by typing

    ./start aneris

  in a terminal.

  You'll see a few windows popup, that's the various Aneris processes.

o Then, start a client by typing

    make r-client

  in a terminal.  This is going to run in your terminal and not pop up
  a new window.

o The client is going to ask "sending?", type "y" for "yes".
